item.description:
 &lt;p&gt;I am thrilled to share my recent experience as a participant in the Doctoral Consortium at ICIS 2023, hosted in the vibrant city of Hyderabad, India. This post is my reflection on the invaluable moments and insights gained during this unforgettable event.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;span id=&#34;more&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;justified-gallery&#34; id=&#34;g1&#34;&gt;

