    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div id=&#34;q1&#34; class=&#34;tab-content&#34;&gt;
          &lt;p&gt;  Should I apply for the consortium? What is the correct time to participate?&lt;/p&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;&lt;div id=&#34;a1&#34; class=&#34;tab-content is-hidden&#34;&gt;
          &lt;p&gt;  I highly recommend that you apply for this enriching event, as it will give you a valuable opportunity to present your research, receive feedback from experts, network with peers, and learn from other doctoral students. The ideal time to participate is when you have an initial draft of your dissertation, but you are still open to suggestions and improvements. This way, you can benefit from the constructive criticism and guidance that the consortium provides. However, you can also apply earlier or later in your PhD journey, depending on your goals and needs.&lt;/p&gt;

      &lt;/div&gt;

